    <item>
      <title>特朗普将再次将胡塞武装指定为恐怖分子，推翻拜登的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-will-again-designate-houthis-as-terrorists-reversing-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统周三签署命令，再次将也门胡塞武装组织列为恐怖组织——近四年前拜登政府撤销了这一称号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/trump-will-again-designate-houthis-as-terrorists-reversing-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 00:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默将遏制英国法庭挑战，以“解除邻避运动的武装”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/starmer-to-curb-uk-court-challenges-to-disarm-the-nimbys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 宣布了防止法律挑战导致重大基础设施项目延误的计划，这是英国政府为让投资者和企业相信其认真追求经济增长而做出的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/starmer-to-curb-uk-court-challenges-to-disarm-the-nimbys</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赦免因追捕致人死亡而被定罪的华盛顿警察</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-pardons-dc-police-officers-convicted-after-fatal-chase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普赦免了两名华盛顿警察安德鲁·扎巴夫斯基和特伦斯·萨顿，他们因追捕一名 20 岁男子后导致其死亡而被定罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/trump-pardons-dc-police-officers-convicted-after-fatal-chase</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:59:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼将在边境增派军队并协助驱逐出境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/pentagon-to-boost-troops-at-border-and-help-with-deportations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国防官员周三表示，五角大楼正在向美国西南边境派遣 1,500 名士兵，多架军用运输机已经在途中，协助驱逐被拜登政府拘留的 5,000 多名移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/pentagon-to-boost-troops-at-border-and-help-with-deportations</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:44:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥称美国对菲律宾的防御承诺“坚定不移”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/us-under-trump-says-philippines-defense-commitments-ironclad</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥表示，华盛顿对菲律宾的防务承诺仍然“坚定不移”，同时批评北京在南海的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/us-under-trump-says-philippines-defense-commitments-ironclad</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治危机下韩国经济艰难增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/south-korea-s-economy-struggles-for-growth-amid-political-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈短暂宣布戒严，在出口增长放缓之际严重打击了消费者信心，导致韩国经济上季度持续低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/south-korea-s-economy-struggles-for-growth-amid-political-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:02:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国将庆祝东南亚首例同性婚礼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/thailand-to-celebrate-southeast-asia-s-first-same-sex-marriages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数百对 LGBTQ 情侣今天将在泰国正式结婚，泰国成为东南亚第一个保障同性伴侣平等婚姻权利的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/thailand-to-celebrate-southeast-asia-s-first-same-sex-marriages</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>五角大楼将向墨西哥边境派遣多达 1,500 名现役军人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-22/urgent-pentagon-to-send-up-to-1-500-active-duty-troops-to-help-secure-us-mexico-border-officials-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿（美联社）——五角大楼周三表示，已开始部署 1,500 名现役军人，帮助确保南部边境安全，实施唐纳德·特朗普总统上任后不久在行政命令中提出的打击移民计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-22/urgent-pentagon-to-send-up-to-1-500-active-duty-troops-to-help-secure-us-mexico-border-officials-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 17:34:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装免费航运船员被关押一年多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/houthis-say-crew-held-captive-for-over-a-year-have-been-freed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞叛军表示，他们已经释放了一年多前劫持的一艘商船的船员，这是缓解红海地区船舶风险的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/houthis-say-crew-held-captive-for-over-a-year-have-been-freed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 13:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪考虑降低关税、增加进口以应对特朗普威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-mulls-lower-tariffs-more-imports-to-counter-trump-s-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果特朗普总统真的采取贸易行动，印度政府将评估包括贸易协议、削减关税和从美国进口更多商品等多种选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/modi-mulls-lower-tariffs-more-imports-to-counter-trump-s-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 06:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
